description: Archer City, Wichita Falls and Olney...these are the lucky Texas towns that get to taste (and then inevitably chase) the delicious street cuisine from this pursuable Food Truck.With terrifically tasty Tacos, Dirty Fries, Nachos, oh my! You’ll want to try everything here... especially the homemade cakes and pie.  Catch this truck if you can and then you too will be a chipper Chasin’ It Fan!
name: Chasin It
